---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import LogoInterra from "../../../assets/images/Logo-Interra.webp";
import InterraIntro from "../../../assets/images/Interra-intro.webp"
---

<section class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-[80px] p-[40px]">
        <div class="size-auto">
           <Image src={InterraIntro} alt="interra intro"/>
        </div>
        <div class="w-[31%] max-lg:w-[40%] max-md:w-[80%] flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-[20px] p-[20px]">
            <Image src={LogoInterra} alt="Logo Interra" />

            <p class="resturant__parrafo text-gray-600">
               built in the late 19th century, is located on the lobby level of the Hotel. Beautiful travertine tables and comfortable iron carved chairs complement the colonial architecture of romantic arches made from dry stone methods. You can enjoy a light lunch before taking your City Tours or simply enjoy the natural, bright ambiance. In the evenings, during dinner, you can immerse yourself in the quiet atmosphere and be delighted by our fine service. You will savor the cuisine of our delectable menus, whose offerings perfectly reflect the elegance of our hotel.
            </p>
            <a class="w-[240px] rounded-[5px] font-normal p-[12px] bg-[#C9A724] items-nav text-white" href="#">
                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf"></i>
                Descarga nuestra Carta
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .resturant__parrafo {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-family: var(--font-family-poppins);
    }
</style>
